This repository was modified to support the Star Pattern Fragment extension.

We added to following package from a modified version of the HDT repository:
src/org/rdfhdt/*

We modified the following files:
src/org/linkeddatafragments/datasource/HdtDataSource.java
src/org/linkeddatafragments/datasource/DataSourceFactory.java
src/org/linkeddatafragments/servlet/TriplePatternFragmentServlet.java

We added the following files:
src/org/linkeddatafragments/datasource/HdtPPDataSource.java

